{"tid":1775152,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"{海外文宣] World pres photo 2020 現正接受提交作品","createTime":"2019-12-08T16:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T16:21:10.000Z","uid":38218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a20c9c0a2ea258fd8d6dd3c79c7e1f8a244039","tid":1775152,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:10:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Connecting the world to the stories that matter</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GWiLVpBizEs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGWiLVpBizEs&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2Ldf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=40d8a051\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GWiLVpBizEs</a><br />\n呢半年黎，香港人經歷咗大大小小嘅公民抗爭<br />\n亦充當唔同嘅角色<br />\n相信不少攝台巴絲都有去紀錄低好多重要嘅時刻<br />\n如其upload 係個人social platform  <br />\n不如用你地嘅作品話俾全世界聽你所見到嘅角度<br />\n同時亦作為海外文宣<br />\n12月2開始接受提交作品<br />\n1月9 停止登記<br />\n1月14 停收作品<br />\n分咗8個categories<br />\nContemporary Issues, Environment, General News, <br />\nLong-Term Projects, Nature, Portraits, Sports, Spot News<br />\nFor more infor: <a href=\"https://www.worldpressphoto.org/programs/contests/photo-contest/28569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldpressphoto.org%2Fprograms%2Fcontests%2Fphoto-contest%2F28569&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2Ldf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=5989ae4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldpressphoto.org/programs/contests/photo-contest/28569</a><br />\n<br />\n歷年黎得獎嘅作品<br />\n<a href=\"https://worldpressphoto.org/collection/photo-contest\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fworldpressphoto.org%2Fcollection%2Fphoto-contest&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2Ldf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=f1f99814\" target=\"_blank\">https://worldpressphoto.org/collection/photo-contest</a><br />\n1990 Photo Contest, Spot News, Singles, 1st prize<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/5ySqbNSQ/CC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2F5ySqbNSQ%2FCC.png&h=99846128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nby Charlie Cole, <em>Newsweek</em><br />\nNikon FM2, 300 mm, f/4, ISO400"},{"pid":"3617a0aca782a866e502e4153c4ce70426b4cbc3","tid":1775152,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5PLNMOw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5PLNMOw.jpg&h=0eecb9a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oGcPZ8x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoGcPZ8x.jpg&h=2c118546&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}